\c 18
\s UPawuli useKorinte leEfesu
\p
\v 1 Emva kwalezizinto uPawuli wasuka eAtene weza eKorinte\x + 19.1. 1 Kor. 1.2. 2 Kor. 1.1,23. 2 Tim. 4.20. Seb. 18.8. 2 Kor. 6.11.\x*.
\v 2 Wasefica umJuda othile uAkwila\x + 18.18,26. Roma 16.3. 1 Kor. 16.19. 2 Tim. 4.19.\x* ngebizo, owePontusi ngokuzalwa\x + 2.9.\x*, owayesanda ukufika evela eIthaliya, loPrisila umkakhe\x + 18.18,26. Roma 16.3. 1 Kor. 16.19. 2 Tim. 4.19.\x* (ngenxa yokulaya kukaKlawudiyosi\x + 11.28.\x* kokuthi wonke amaJuda kawasuke eRoma), waya kubo;
\v 3 njalo ngoba babelomsebenzi ofananayo, wahlala kubo wasebenza\x + Mat. 25.16. Seb. 20.34. 1 Kor. 4.12. 1 Thes. 2.9. 2 Thes. 3.8.\x*; ngoba babengabenzi bamathente ngomsebenzi.
\v 4 Wasekhulumisana \add labo\x + 17.17.\x*\add* esinagogeni amasabatha wonke\x + 13.14.\x*, wancenga amaJuda lamaGriki.
\v 5 Kwathi uSilasi loTimothi\x + 17.14,15.\x* sebehlile bevela eMakedoniya\x + 16.12.\x*, uPawuli wacindezelwa nguMoya\x + Luka 12.50. Jobe 32.18.\x*, efakaza kumaJuda\x + 20.21. Luka 16.28.\x* ukuthi uJesu unguKristu\x + 17.3. 18.28.\x*.
\v 6 Kwathi emelana laye ehlambaza\x + 13.45.\x*, wathintitha izembatho\x + Neh. 5.13. Mat. 10.14. Seb. 13.51.\x*, wathi kuwo: Igazi lenu \add kalibe\add* phezu kwekhanda lenu\x + Hez. 18.13. 33.4. Levi 20.9.\x*; mina ngimsulwa\x + 20.26. Hez. 3.18,19. 33.9.\x*; kusukela khathesi ngizakuya kwabezizwe\x + 28.28.\x*.
\v 7 Wasesuka lapho waya endlini yomunye obizo lakhe nguJustusi, okhonza uNkulunkulu, ondlu yakhe yayiseduze lesinagoge\x + 16.14. 13.43.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa uKrispusi\x + 1 Kor. 1.14.\x* umphathi wesinagoge wakholwa eNkosini\x + 18.17. Mark. 5.22.\x* lendlu yakhe yonke\x + 11.14.\x*; labanengi kwabeKorinte balalela bakholwa babhabhathizwa\x + 19.1. 1 Kor. 1.2. 2 Kor. 1.1,23. 2 Tim. 4.20. Seb. 18.8. 2 Kor. 6.11.\x*.
\v 9 INkosi yasisithi kuPawuli ebusuku\x + 23.11. 27.23,24.\x* ngombono\x + 12.9.\x*: Ungesabi, kodwa khuluma njalo ungathuli;
\v 10 ngoba mina ngilawe\x + Jer. 1.8,19. Mat. 28.20. Josh. 1.5.\x*, njalo kakho ozakuhlasela ukukwenzela okubi; ngoba ngilabantu abanengi kulumuzi.
\v 11 Njalo wahlala umnyaka lenyanga eziyisithupha, efundisa ilizwi likaNkulunkulu phakathi kwabo.
