\v 12 Kwathi uGaliyo engumbusi\x + 13.7.\x* weAkaya\x + 18.27. 19.21. Roma 15.26. 16.5. 1 Kor. 16.15. 2 Kor. 1.1. 9.2. 11.10. 1 Thes. 1.7,8.\x*, amaJuda amvukela uPawuli nganhliziyonye, amusa\x + Mat. 10.18.\x* phambi kwesihlalo sokwahlulela\x + 18.16,17. Mat. 27.19.\x*,
\v 13 esithi: Lo uncenga abantu ukuthi bakhonze uNkulunkulu ngokuphambene lomlayo\x + 18.15.\x*.
\v 14 Kodwa kwathi uPawuli esezavula umlomo\x + Mat. 5.2.\x*, uGaliyo wathi kumaJuda: Ngakho uba bekulento engalunganga kumbe inkohliso embi\x + 13.10.\x*, maJuda, ngesizatho bengizalibekezelela\x + Mat. 17.17.\x*;
\v 15 kodwa uba kuyikuphikisana ngelizwi lamabizo\x + 23.29. 25.19.\x*, lomlayo phakathi kwenu\x + 18.15.\x*, ziboneleni lina; ngoba mina kangithandi ukuba ngumahluleli walezizinto.
\v 16 Wasewaxotsha esihlalweni sokwahlulela\x + 18.16,17. Mat. 27.19.\x*.
\v 17 Wonke amaGriki asebamba uSostenesi\x + 1 Kor. 1.1.\x* umphathi wesinagoge\x + 18.8.\x*, a\add m\add*tshaya phambi kwesihlalo sokwahlulela\x + 18.16,17. Mat. 27.19.\x*. Njalo uGaliyo kaze azinanza lezizinto.
