\v 18 Kwathi uPawuli esahlezi insuku ezinengi, wavalelisa abazalwane\x + 18.21. Luka 9.61.\x*, wasuka ngomkhumbi waya eSiriya\x + Mat. 4.24. Luka 2.2. Seb. 15.23,41. 20.3. 21.3. Gal. 1.21.\x*, loPrisila\x + 18.1,26.\x* loAkwila\x + 18.1,26.\x* kanye laye, esephuce ikhanda\x + Nani 6.18. Seb. 21.24.\x* eKenikreya\x + Roma 16.1.\x*, ngoba wayelesifungo\x + Nani 6.18. Seb. 21.24.\x*.
\v 19 Sebefikile eEfesu\x + 18.21,24. 19.1,17,26. 20.16,17. 1 Kor. 15.32. 16.8. Efe. 1.1. 1 Tim. 1.3. 2 Tim. 1.18. 4.12. Isam. 1.11. Seb. 21.29. Isam. 2.1.\x*, wasebatshiya khona; kodwa yena engena esinagogeni\x + 13.14.\x* wakhulumisana lamaJuda\x + 17.17.\x*.
\v 20 Sebemcelile ukuthi ahlale isikhathi esidanyana labo, kavumanga;
\v 21 kodwa wabavalelisa\x + 18.21. Luka 9.61.\x* esithi: Kufanele isibili\x + 20.16.\x* ukuthi ngigcine eJerusalema umkhosi ozayo\x + Mat. 26.18.\x*; kodwa ngizabuyela kini njalo, uba uNkulunkulu evuma\x + 1 Kor. 4.19. 16.7. Heb. 6.3. Jak. 4.15. Roma 15.32.\x*. Wasuka eEfesu ngomkhumbi\x + 18.21,24. 19.1,17,26. 20.16,17. 1 Kor. 15.32. 16.8. Efe. 1.1. 1 Tim. 1.3. 2 Tim. 1.18. 4.12. Isam. 1.11. Seb. 21.29. Isam. 2.1.\x*,
\v 22 njalo esefikile eKesariya\x + 8.40.\x*, wenyuka wabingelela ibandla\x + 21.12,15.\x*; wehlela eAntiyoki\x + 11.26.\x*.
\s Uhambo lwesithathu lukaPawuli. UApolo eEfesu
\p
\v 23 Njalo esechithe isikhathi esithile, wasuka, wadabula ngokulandelana ilizwe leGalathiya\x + 16.6. Gal. 4.14.\x* leFrigiya\x + 2.10.\x*, eqinisa bonke\x + 14.22.\x*\x + Luka 1.3.\x* abafundi\x + 18.27. 11.26.\x*.
