\v 24 Njalo umJuda othile, uApolosi ngebizo\x + 19.1. 1 Kor. 1.12. 3.4,5,6,22. 4.6. 16.12. Tit. 3.13.\x*, umAleksandriya\x + 6.9.\x* ngokuzalwa, eyindoda eyisikhulumi, wafika eEfesu\x + Luka 1.4.\x*, elamandla emibhalweni.
\v 25 Lo wayefundisiwe indlela yeNkosi, njalo evutha emoyeni\x + Roma 12.11.\x* wakhuluma wafundisa ngokukhuthala izinto ezimayelana leNkosi\x + 18.26. 23.15,20. 24.22.\x*, esazi ubhabhathizo lukaJohane kuphela\x + Luka 7.29. Seb. 19.3.\x*;
\v 26 lo waseqala ukukhuluma ngesibindi esinagogeni\x + 4.29.\x*. Kwathi sebemzwile uPrisila loAkwila\x + 18.1,18.\x*, bamthathela kubo, bamchasisela\x + 11.4.\x* indlela kaNkulunkulu\x + 9.2.\x* ngokuqonda okukhulu\x + 18.26. 23.15,20. 24.22.\x*.
\v 27 Kwathi esethanda ukuchaphela eAkaya\x + 18.12.\x*, abazalwane be\add m\add*khuthaza babhalela abafundi ukuthi bamemukele\x + Luka 8.40.\x*; okwathi esefikile wabasiza kakhulu abakholwa ngomusa\x + 1 Kor. 3.6.\x*;
\v 28 ngoba waphikisa ngamandla\x + Luka 23.10.\x* wawehlula ngokupheleleyo obala amaJuda\x + 17.2.\x*, etshengisa ngemibhalo\x + 17.2.\x* ukuthi uKristu unguJesu\x + 18.5. 17.3. 9.22.\x*.
